Please issue an update!

I'm a die hard formula one fan . Having bought a ps3 for the launch title release . A ps vita for again at the time a launch release . So I was excited to see this available for the android - the graphics are amazing . Truly amazing what they have achieved to deliver the graphics . One thing that really disappoints me is the controls . If you like touch screen or tilt controls you won't mind but to drive a f1 car it is very precise how you drove the car and have certain lines on the track to follow . I could drive the car with assists on only and that takes alot of the skill out of driving the car for me . I got a mad catz lynx 3 controller and was excited to use it for the game but found out it doesn't support it at all . Surely a fame of this magnitude would be using accessories galore and to enjoy the game much more . An update would be fantastic and I would give it 4 / 5 then .
